{"tid":2391026,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俄國智障孤兒影型男寫真紅爆廣告界 摯友攝影師扭轉他險死人生","createTime":"2021-02-02T03:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T03:15:08.000Z","uid":382478,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf0d0ee493ba76b5d78b2e27461b44f93bca228","tid":2391026,"uid":382478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"出外真係靠朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全靠個朋友幫佢爆紅，改寫佢人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想要個咁嘅朋友。。。<br />\n<br />\n//現實往往比電影情節更荒謬。俄羅斯一名智障孤兒Yury，出生後便逼父母棄在孤兒院門前，長大後離開孤兒院，無依無靠流落街頭，更遇上騙子。這些壞份子不但操控他做無薪的勞動工作，更加誘騙他到銀行借錢，可憐的Yury不懂世途險惡，誤以為對方是真誠的朋友需要金錢應急，就白白被騙走約7萬港元金錢。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FW2BNW1xrGb.DSJ_0iftsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/n34355566767img.ws_.126.net_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFW2BNW1xrGb.DSJ_0iftsg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2Fn34355566767img.ws_.126.net_.jpg&h=a5a2b66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S4c5ScCtf3C4CAfpGe5ZvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/PSX_20210120_120027-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FS4c5ScCtf3C4CAfpGe5ZvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FPSX_20210120_120027-1024x576.jpg&h=55f9b2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/errCbvqGNqverdFTYe_P7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/139761710_1070456400048001_1168895882789347319_n_1024-820x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FerrCbvqGNqverdFTYe_P7A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F139761710_1070456400048001_1168895882789347319_n_1024-820x1024.jpg&h=da131c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//Roman最擅長的是攝影，於是他讓Yury當起他的模特兒，拍攝一連串的寫真照，發佈到社交平台為他眾籌。Yury的五官非常上鏡，清潔工造型被讚有型，而穿上西裝更是十分高大帥氣。這輯寫真引起網上極大迴響，成功為他眾籌兩倍目標金額。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/l3bmXzTdqIHWitUASqY6XQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/87876555nimg.ws_.126.net_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fl3bmXzTdqIHWitUASqY6XQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F87876555nimg.ws_.126.net_.jpg&h=5197748a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%AD%A4%E5%85%92%E5%BD%B1%E5%9E%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%AF%AB%E7%9C%9F%E7%B4%85%E7%88%86%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%95%8C-%E6%91%AF%E5%8F%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E6%89%AD%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%96%E9%9A%AA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F-183746001.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2599%25BA%25E9%259A%259C%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2595%258C-%25E6%2591%25AF%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2589%25AD%25E8%25BD%2589%25E4%25BB%2596%25E9%259A%25AA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F-183746001.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BOIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=56153dc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%AD%A4%E5%85%92%E5%BD%B1%E5%9E%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%AF%AB%E7%9C%9F%E7%B4%85%E7%88%86%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%95%8C-%E6%91%AF%E5%8F%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E6%89%AD%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%96%E9%9A%AA%E6